{"tid":345753,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"認真，肥婆搞到我差啲以為自己有面盲症。","createTime":"2017-08-03T10:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T11:54:12.000Z","uid":35370,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d25c18334886ee6ad016ef31479500ac70023553","tid":345753,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"點解啲肥婆可以個個都差唔多樣？<br />\n解釋下件事先，今日放Lunch係公司附近食飯<br />\n肥婆同個男人過嚟搭檯<br />\n婆婆媽媽咁拉櫈坐，我抬頭一望以為係我公司某個肥婆上司<br />\n唔係喎，但望多幾望又好似唔係，好亂<br />\n減薪就大鑊啦，於是我都唔知同唔同佢打招呼<br />\n肥婆之後成餐飯冇理我，咁我先知道佢唔係公司個件<br />\n呀，真係鬆一口氣"},{"pid":"222e5d025ef091d4cb1c3a80d3e29da7bd527766","tid":345753,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:53:13.000Z","msg":"肥婆留低負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0be9b1edcab2e7735267c4a7353f32ea4886a6","tid":345753,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"留意到叫親Ruby都系肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e68145018e591a964f64b92f2469385a90f518","tid":345753,"uid":21102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留意到叫親Ruby都系肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n系你老母呀死肥婆 捐返入你老母個閪窿度啦"},{"pid":"3242a3147897713c9624f076676e53d0771098c5","tid":345753,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留意到叫親Ruby都系肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n系你老母呀死肥婆 捐返入你老母個閪窿度啦</blockquote><br />\n咁都比佢騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b6f1c3c93b067a619f95e7fcc3ee3b7fdcff8d","tid":34